Definition: a white male Southerner with an unpretentious convivial manner and conservative or intolerant attitudes and a strong sense of fellowship with and loyalty to other members of his peer group
Synonyms: good_ole_boy, good_ol, _boy, white_man, Southerner, a, white, male, with, an, unpretentious, convivial, manner, and, conservative, or, intolerant, attitudes, strong, sense, of, fellowship, loyalty, to, other, members, his, peer, group
Category: noun.person
